data.description:

They have set up Louieâ€™s Trust a charity dedicated to supporting families with sick children in the hospital, helping to ease their burden during the most difficult times. Louieâ€™s Legacy aims to be a lifeline for those facing unimaginable challenges.

No family should struggle alone while caring for a sick child. By donating, you can help provide practical and emotional support to those who need it most.

This year Iâ€™m running the GNR to raise money for this amazing charity.
Please donate today.
Every contribution, big or small, makes a difference. Letâ€™s honor Louie by bringing light to others in their darkest moments.

data.name: Megan Sutton
data.description:
This charity holds a special place not only to me but also to anyone who came across Louie with his infectious smile and his loving family.  

I was very fortunate to be apart of Louieâ€™s care and despite all the challenges this family unfortunately faced they never once let their smiles slip. They have gone and created this charity in remembrance of Louie to now help other children and their families who also face struggles whilst in hospital. I want to help show that Louieâ€™s memories continue to live on in us all and help those who face similar circumstances. It will also be an achievement for myself who is not a runner and stepping well out of my comfort zone but what better charity to run for than â€˜Louieâ€™s Trustâ€™.  Any contribution is greatly appreciated and will help brighten someoneâ€™s day.

data.description:

What they have created in their beautiful boyâ€™s name is nothing short of amazing. Their dedication to making a difference for others is truly inspiring, and I want to do my part to support their mission and the incredible impact they have on so many families.

So please donate every little helps! 

Thank you! â¤ï¸
